  PLAYMATE LABS — PAGE ASSIGNMENT GUIDE
  File: snippets/page-assignments.liquid

  ============================================================
  HOW TO ASSIGN TEMPLATES TO PAGES IN SHOPIFY ADMIN
  ============================================================

  Every URL below needs a matching Page created in Shopify Admin
  → Online Store → Pages → Add page.

  Then set the TEMPLATE SUFFIX on that page to match.

  URL Handle          │ Template to Assign              │ Notes
  ────────────────────┼─────────────────────────────────┼──────────────────────────────
  /pages/drops        │ page.drops                      │ Monthly Drops hub
  /pages/monthly-drops│ page.monthly-drops              │ Alias — same content
  /pages/experience   │ page.experience                 │ 5-Day Sensory Experience
  /pages/5-day-experience│ page.5-day-experience        │ Alias — same content
  /pages/events       │ page.events                     │ Events listing
  /pages/event-detail │ page.event-detail               │ Single event (add ?id= param)
  /pages/community    │ page.community                  │ Membership & community hub
  /pages/about        │ page.about                      │ About Playmate Labs
  /pages/journal      │ page.journal                    │ Journal / Explore landing
  /pages/shop         │ page.shop                       │ Custom shop landing
  /pages/faq          │ page.faq                        │ FAQ / Help
  /pages/contact      │ page.contact                    │ Contact form
  /pages/gifts        │ page.gifts                      │ Gift guide
  /pages/stockists    │ page.stockists                  │ Find in store
  /pages/privacy-policy│ page.privacy                  │ Privacy policy
  /pages/terms        │ page.terms                      │ Terms & Conditions
  /pages/download     │ page.download                   │ Internal theme download ref

  COLLECTION PAGES (no page needed — use Collections):
  /collections/all                                       │ All products
  /collections/monthly-drops                            │ Monthly drop kits
  /collections/consumables                              │ Consumables category
  /collections/date-night-kits                          │ Date night kits

  CUSTOMER PAGES (handled by Shopify automatically):
  /account                → templates/customers/account.liquid
  /account/login          → templates/customers/login.liquid
  /account/register       → templates/customers/register.liquid
  /account/orders/[id]    → templates/customers/order.liquid (Shopify default)
  /account/addresses      → templates/customers/addresses.liquid (Shopify default)

  BLOG / JOURNAL (uses Shopify blog system):
  /blogs/journal          → templates/blog.liquid
  /blogs/journal/[article]→ templates/article.liquid

  ============================================================
  SIDEBAR / INTERNAL LINK REFERENCE
  ============================================================

  Account Dashboard sidebar links:
  - Overview    → /account (customers/account.liquid tab=overview)
  - Rewards     → /account?tab=rewards
  - Orders      → /account?tab=orders
  - Events      → /account?tab=events
  - Drops       → /account?tab=drops
  - Profile     → /account?tab=profile

  Community page sidebar links:
  - Community   → /pages/community
  - Membership  → /pages/community#tiers
  - Rewards     → /pages/community#rewards
  - Join        → /pages/community#community-join

  Navigation links (set in Shopify Admin → Navigation → Main Menu):
  - Shop         → /collections/all
  - Monthly Drops→ /pages/drops
  - 5-Day Experience→ /pages/experience
  - Events       → /pages/events
  - Journal      → /blogs/journal
  - About        → /pages/about
  - Community    → /pages/community

